@Bill 

Hope that by now you've donated (ha) blood and had a nice  breakfast.  Hate those fasting tests!  When PhysDau was having one of her (dozens and dozens) of fasting lab appts, I used to skip breakfast with her (Solidarity!)  It is hard to face a very young child otherwise.  
My breakfast was late this morning because DHubby slept in.  It was SO tempting to accidentally drop an aluminum mixing bowl onto the tile floor.....

